    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large dry pan over a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Once golden, add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>romesco sauce </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>and cook for 2 min further or until the sauce has reduced and the breadcrumbs are crisp \u2013 these are your <strong>romesco breadcrumbs</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/catalan-style-smoky-king-prawns-mafaldine-and-romesco-crunch/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>pasta</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>pasta</strong> for 7-9 min (10\u201312 min for wholewheat) or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>pasta</strong>, reserving a cup of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/catalan-style-smoky-king-prawns-mafaldine-and-romesco-crunch/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the pasta cooks, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and roughly dice</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/catalan-style-smoky-king-prawns-mafaldine-and-romesco-crunch/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced pepper </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to soften</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/catalan-style-smoky-king-prawns-mafaldine-and-romesco-crunch/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika </strong>and <strong>tomato paste</strong> and cook for 2 min or until fragrant</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/catalan-style-smoky-king-prawns-mafaldine-and-romesco-crunch/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, drain then add your <strong>king prawns </strong>to the pan</p><p>Cook for 4-5 min further or until cooked through</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/catalan-style-smoky-king-prawns-mafaldine-and-romesco-crunch/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the prawns are cooked, add the <strong>cooked pasta </strong>to the pan with 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[170ml] </span><strong>reserved starchy pasta water</strong>, your <strong>balsamic sun-dried tomato paste</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>remaining romesco sauce</strong></p><p>Finish with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>Catalan-style</strong> <strong>smoky king prawn pasta</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/catalan-style-smoky-king-prawns-mafaldine-and-romesco-crunch/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Catalan-style</strong> <strong>smoky king prawn pasta </strong>and garnish with the <strong>romesco crumb</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
